⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Cortisone Shot
node VBL · VBL · ⟦The Cortisone Shot:VBL:fed969⟧

WHO   — The Cortisone Shot — the needle · the cost made literal
WHAT  — Numb the pain, tape it up, send the body back in. True as a metaphor for the W's price; exaggerated as a real practice for minors.
WHERE — VBL · Varsity Blues (1999)  Framework inputs: Varsity Blues (1999, dir. Brian Robbins, MTV Films/Paramount); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the whole film is in one image: the needle that buys one more banner with a teenager's knee.
HOW   — By masking the injury instead of treating it — winning now, paying later, on someone else's body.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Numb it, tape it, send it back in. I am the price of Friday night, paid in advance by a seventeen-year-old's knee.

